<span id="freeTextContainer8739520427574266120">Betrayal in Black<br/>By<br/>Mark M Bello<br/><br/>My Review:<br/>Being a fan of legal thrillers, I have picked Mark M Bello&apos;s couple of novels and I loved each one of them. Betrayal in Black is the fourth installment in the Zachary Blake Legal Thriller series. <br/><br/>Two young black men robbed a Burger King. Police are looking for them. When Marcus, a black man, was returning from a fair with his family, patrol officer Jones, who was on duty at that time, suspected Marcus as the Burger King suspect. On the officer&apos;s order, Ma</span>
  <span id="freeText8739520427574266120" style="display:none">Betrayal in Black<br />By<br />Mark M Bello<br /><br />My Review:<br />Being a fan of legal thrillers, I have picked Mark M Bello's couple of novels and I loved each one of them. Betrayal in Black is the fourth installment in the Zachary Blake Legal Thriller series. <br /><br />Two young black men robbed a Burger King. Police are looking for them. When Marcus, a black man, was returning from a fair with his family, patrol officer Jones, who was on duty at that time, suspected Marcus as the Burger King suspect. On the officer's order, Marcus pulled his car. But his wife Sarah told him to inform the cop in advance about a legal gun that he carries. When Marcus was taking out the licence and registration, Jones thought that he was pulling out the gun. Here, the mistake is totally of Officer Jones as he had given two orders to Marcus at the same time and he could obviously follow one order at a time. <br /><br />Marcus was shot by an officer for not following his command. Whatever Jones had done isn't write. Will people go on protest as the deceased was black and the officer who shot is a White? This is a nail-biting story. The twists and turns in the story helped me to enjoy this book more. Writing style is brilliant. He describes the world created by him in detail. Please be advised that this book has sensitive topics. It is a story worth reading. Grab this right now.<br /><br />My Rating: 5/5</span>
