    <a title="Beth Birnbaum" class="left imgcol" href="/user/show/67534218-beth-birnbaum"><img alt="Beth Birnbaum" src="https://s.gr-assets.com/assets/nophoto/user/u_50x66-632230dc9882b4352d753eedf9396530.png" /></a>

